news.name: Misprint of Ordis version Moth Collision
news.answer: The first printing of the Rare, Ordis version of Moth Collision mistakenly read  "[Fleeting].  If you control a #Soldier#, I cost #{2} less.# Discard target Character #with Hand Cost {3} or less.#".  The correct version says  "[Fleeting].  If you control a #Soldier,# I cost {1} less.  Discard target Character."
news.question: Did the text of this card change?
